result.notes: This survey was undertaken by Cefas as part of the CEFAS Historic surveys; ... Survey took place between 31/08/1908 and 18/09/1908 on Huxley Equipment used during this survey : - Beam Trawl 2m shrimp net fryma liner 3 chains x - Benthic Sampling Gear Conical Dredge Plymouth fine mesh - Grimsby style otter trawl Codend with mesh 6.8cm - Lowestoft smack beam trawl 43ft 13.1m Survey operations were undertaken on 20 stations 34 different species were caught on this survey
